      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Feishu `extractEmojiOnly()` helper and uses it when composing `identity.emoji` card headers in outbound and reply-dispatcher paths.\n\nPR surface: Source +21. Total +21 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level. Current main concatenates raw `identity.emoji` into Feishu card headers, and the PR-head sanitizer can be directly shown to split flags and skin-tone emoji.",
